title: Las Vegas → San Francisco
content:
Left our hotel in Vegas a bit after 10am to get to the airport. Timed things pretty well again and had just enough time to have a bite to eat for lunch before we had to get to the gate. Flight was very smooth, just a little delayed at each airport sitting on the tarmac.

San Francisco is immediately a more interesting city than we have been to so far. Rested in the hotel room and figured out what to have for dinner - Italian at Fisherman’s Wharf - some of the best well priced Italian I have had :)
